CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, July 28, 1956, pg. A19 reads: "Happy Students - This trio was among the students receiving awards at the annual Metoka Club Scholarship Garden Party. They are Marian Brown, Ada Barbour and Mary Lesesne. - "Teenie" Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait, left to right: Marian Brown, Ada Barbour and Mary Lesesne, standing at gazing ball for Metoka Club Scholarship Garden Party
